    "For example, individuals with insulin resistance may perceive sweetness differently or experience altered satiety signals, affecting their preference for sweet flavors (Tarragon and Moreno 2018).",
    "By monitoring these physiological indicators, AI systems can dynamically adapt meal plans to suggest alternative flavor profiles.",
    "Such personalized recommendations fulfill nutritional requirements without sacrificing taste satisfaction.",
    "Additionally, demographic groups like older adults and children may have distinct taste sensitivities, requiring models that can adapt to age-related changes (Braun et al. 2022).",
    "Behavioral data and evolving preferences further contribute to taste personalization."
